summary: Ambitious, detail-oriented management professional with international experience in service delivery in a variety of fields such as the food and beverage industry, marketing, education, and film. Multi-faceted and efficient with cross-level communication skills and experience in providing superb organization and management support. Highly skilled in coordinating complex projects and supervising teams while increasing efficiency, exceeding goals and objectives, and fostering professional relationships. Multilingual (English, Spanish, and French) professional with expertise in mastering skills and improving processes.
